{
  "video_id": "XZiNVGA78kA",
  "title": "\"Good\" and \"bad\" are incomplete stories we tell ourselves | Heather Lanier",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12900.0,
      "end_time": 16991.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s an ancient parable about a farmer who lost his horse."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17150.0,
      "end_time": 20389.0,
      "text": "And neighbors came over to say, \"Oh, that&#39;s too bad.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20413.0,
      "end_time": 23782.0,
      "text": "And the farmer said, \"Good or bad, hard to say.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24649.0,
      "end_time": 30159.0,
      "text": "Days later, the horse returns and brings with it seven wild horses."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 30183.0,
      "end_time": 33800.0,
      "text": "And neighbors come over to say, \"Oh, that&#39;s so good!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 33824.0,
      "end_time": 38929.0,
      "text": "And the farmer just shrugs and says, \"Good or bad, hard to say.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 39579.0,
      "end_time": 43651.0,
      "text": "The next day, the farmer&#39;s son rides one of the wild horses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 43675.0,
      "end_time": 46160.0,
      "text": "is thrown off and breaks his leg."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 46185.0,
      "end_time": 49490.0,
      "text": "And the neighbors say, \"Oh, that&#39;s terrible luck.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 49514.0,
      "end_time": 53621.0,
      "text": "And the farmer says, \"Good or bad, hard to say.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 54587.0,
      "end_time": 57258.0,
      "text": "Eventually, officers come knocking on people&#39;s doors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 57282.0,
      "end_time": 59940.0,
      "text": "looking for men to draft for an army,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 59965.0,
      "end_time": 63538.0,
      "text": "and they see the farmer&#39;s son and his leg and they pass him by."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 63562.0,
      "end_time": 66118.0,
      "text": "And neighbors say, \"Ooh, that&#39;s great luck!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 66142.0,
      "end_time": 70630.0,
      "text": "And the farmer says, \"Good or bad, hard to say.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 71136.0,
      "end_time": 73583.0,
      "text": "I first heard this story 20 years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 73607.0,
      "end_time": 76194.0,
      "text": "and I have since applied it 100 times."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 76218.0,
      "end_time": 78143.0,
      "text": "Didn&#39;t get the job I wanted:"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 78734.0,
      "end_time": 80143.0,
      "text": "good or bad, hard to say."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 80905.0,
      "end_time": 83274.0,
      "text": "Got the job I wanted:"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 83298.0,
      "end_time": 85425.0,
      "text": "good or bad, hard to say."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 85972.0,
      "end_time": 89226.0,
      "text": "To me, the story is not about looking on the bright side"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 89250.0,
      "end_time": 91636.0,
      "text": "or waiting to see how things turn out."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 92550.0,
      "end_time": 95738.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s about how eager we can be to label a situation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 95762.0,
      "end_time": 98544.0,
      "text": "to put concrete around it by judging it."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 98901.0,
      "end_time": 101967.0,
      "text": "But reality is much more fluid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 101992.0,
      "end_time": 106838.0,
      "text": "and good and bad are often incomplete stories that we tell ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 106862.0,
      "end_time": 109252.0,
      "text": "The parable has been my warning"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 109276.0,
      "end_time": 112899.0,
      "text": "that by gripping tightly to the story of good or bad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 112924.0,
      "end_time": 116678.0,
      "text": "I close down my ability to truly see a situation."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 116702.0,
      "end_time": 120312.0,
      "text": "I learn more when I proceed and loosen my grip"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 120336.0,
      "end_time": 123634.0,
      "text": "and proceed openly with curiosity and wonder."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 124415.0,
      "end_time": 127490.0,
      "text": "But seven years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 127730.0,
      "end_time": 129172.0,
      "text": "when I was pregnant with my first child,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 129196.0,
      "end_time": 132160.0,
      "text": "I completely forgot this lesson."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 132471.0,
      "end_time": 135620.0,
      "text": "I believed I knew wholeheartedly what was good."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 135644.0,
      "end_time": 137353.0,
      "text": "When it came to having kids,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 137377.0,
      "end_time": 140889.0,
      "text": "I thought that good was some version of a superbaby,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 140913.0,
      "end_time": 144877.0,
      "text": "some ultrahealthy human who possessed not a single flaw"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 144901.0,
      "end_time": 149650.0,
      "text": "and would practically wear a cape flying into her superhero future."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 149674.0,
      "end_time": 154421.0,
      "text": "I took DHA pills to ensure that my baby had a super-high-functioning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 154445.0,
      "end_time": 155730.0,
      "text": "supersmart brain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 155754.0,
      "end_time": 158427.0,
      "text": "and I ate mostly organic food,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 158451.0,
      "end_time": 161600.0,
      "text": "and I trained for a medication-free labor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 161300.0,
      "end_time": 162851.0,
      "text": "and I did many other things"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 162875.0,
      "end_time": 167101.0,
      "text": "because I thought these things would help me make not just a good baby,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 167125.0,
      "end_time": 169590.0,
      "text": "but the best baby possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 170693.0,
      "end_time": 175382.0,
      "text": "When my daughter Fiona was born, she weighed 4 pounds, 12 ounces,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 175406.0,
      "end_time": 178182.0,
      "text": "or 2.15 kilograms."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 178514.0,
      "end_time": 182406.0,
      "text": "The pediatrician said there were only two possible explanations"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 182430.0,
      "end_time": 184480.0,
      "text": "for her tiny size."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 184720.0,
      "end_time": 187157.0,
      "text": "\"Either,\" he said, \"it&#39;s bad seed,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 187744.0,
      "end_time": 189363.0,
      "text": "\"or it&#39;s bad soil.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 189773.0,
      "end_time": 194616.0,
      "text": "And I wasn&#39;t so tired from labor to lose the thread of his logic:"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 194640.0,
      "end_time": 196934.0,
      "text": "my newborn, according to the doctor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 196959.0,
      "end_time": 198653.0,
      "text": "was a bad plant."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 199873.0,
      "end_time": 204132.0,
      "text": "Eventually, I learned that my daughter had an ultra-rare chromosomal condition"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 204156.0,
      "end_time": 206172.0,
      "text": "called Wolf-Hirschhorn syndrome."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 206196.0,
      "end_time": 209400.0,
      "text": "She was missing a chunk of her fourth chromosome."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 209830.0,
      "end_time": 213150.0,
      "text": "And although my daughter was good --"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 213390.0,
      "end_time": 214396.0,
      "text": "she was alive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 214420.0,
      "end_time": 216476.0,
      "text": "and she had brand new baby skin"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 216501.0,
      "end_time": 219944.0,
      "text": "and the most aware onyx eyes --"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 219968.0,
      "end_time": 222880.0,
      "text": "I also learned that people with her syndrome"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 222112.0,
      "end_time": 225406.0,
      "text": "have significant developmental delays and disabilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 225430.0,
      "end_time": 228234.0,
      "text": "Some never learn to walk or talk."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 228747.0,
      "end_time": 232152.0,
      "text": "I did not have the equanimity of the farmer."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 232176.0,
      "end_time": 236153.0,
      "text": "The situation looked unequivocally bad to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 236177.0,
      "end_time": 239404.0,
      "text": "But here&#39;s where the parable is so useful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 239428.0,
      "end_time": 244429.0,
      "text": "because for weeks after her diagnosis, I felt gripped by despair,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 244453.0,
      "end_time": 248269.0,
      "text": "locked in the story that all of this was tragic."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 248293.0,
      "end_time": 252580.0,
      "text": "Reality, though -- thankfully -- is much more fluid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 252820.0,
      "end_time": 254672.0,
      "text": "and it has much more to teach."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 255413.0,
      "end_time": 260180.0,
      "text": "As I started to get to know this mysterious person who was my kid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 260204.0,
      "end_time": 264357.0,
      "text": "my fixed, tight story of tragedy loosened."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 264381.0,
      "end_time": 266750.0,
      "text": "It turned out my girl loved reggae,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 266774.0,
      "end_time": 270686.0,
      "text": "and she would smirk when my husband would bounce her tiny body up and down"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 270710.0,
      "end_time": 271890.0,
      "text": "to the rhythm."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 271914.0,
      "end_time": 276599.0,
      "text": "Her onyx eyes eventually turned the most stunning Lake Tahoe blue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 276624.0,
      "end_time": 280990.0,
      "text": "and she loved using them to gaze intently into other people&#39;s eyes."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 281376.0,
      "end_time": 285183.0,
      "text": "At five months old, she could not hold her head up like other babies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 285207.0,
      "end_time": 288194.0,
      "text": "but she could hold this deep, intent eye contact."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 288568.0,
      "end_time": 292876.0,
      "text": "One friend said, \"She&#39;s the most aware baby I&#39;ve ever seen.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 293513.0,
      "end_time": 297477.0,
      "text": "But where I saw the gift of her calm, attentive presence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 297502.0,
      "end_time": 301855.0,
      "text": "an occupational therapist who came over to our house to work with Fiona"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 301879.0,
      "end_time": 304641.0,
      "text": "saw a child who was neurologically dull."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 304665.0,
      "end_time": 307941.0,
      "text": "This therapist was especially disappointed"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 307965.0,
      "end_time": 310344.0,
      "text": "that Fiona wasn&#39;t rolling over yet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 310369.0,
      "end_time": 313628.0,
      "text": "and so she told me we needed to wake her neurology up."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 313652.0,
      "end_time": 316570.0,
      "text": "One day she leaned over my daughter&#39;s body,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 316595.0,
      "end_time": 318890.0,
      "text": "took her tiny shoulders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 318113.0,
      "end_time": 320977.0,
      "text": "jostled her and said, \"Wake up! Wake up!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 321738.0,
      "end_time": 324839.0,
      "text": "We had a few therapists visit our house that first year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 324863.0,
      "end_time": 328589.0,
      "text": "and they usually focused on what they thought was bad about my kid."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 328613.0,
      "end_time": 331543.0,
      "text": "I was really happy when Fiona started using her right hand"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 331567.0,
      "end_time": 334296.0,
      "text": "to bully a dangling stuffed sheep,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 334320.0,
      "end_time": 338300.0,
      "text": "but the therapist was fixated on my child&#39;s left hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 338270.0,
      "end_time": 341119.0,
      "text": "Fiona had a tendency not to use this hand very often,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 341143.0,
      "end_time": 344100.0,
      "text": "and she would cross the fingers on that hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 344350.0,
      "end_time": 346935.0,
      "text": "So the therapist said we should devise a splint,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 346959.0,
      "end_time": 351104.0,
      "text": "which would rob my kid of the ability to actually use those fingers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 351128.0,
      "end_time": 354715.0,
      "text": "but it would at least force them into some position that looked normal."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 355516.0,
      "end_time": 358476.0,
      "text": "In that first year, I was starting to realize a few things."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 358500.0,
      "end_time": 362418.0,
      "text": "One: ancient parables aside, my kid had some bad therapists."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 362442.0,
      "end_time": 363491.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 363515.0,
      "end_time": 365147.0,
      "text": "Two: I had a choice."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 365171.0,
      "end_time": 369265.0,
      "text": "Like a person offered to swallow a red pill or a blue pill,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 369289.0,
      "end_time": 372897.0,
      "text": "I could choose to see my daughter&#39;s differences as bad;"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 372922.0,
      "end_time": 376250.0,
      "text": "I could strive toward the goal that her therapists called,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 376274.0,
      "end_time": 377460.0,
      "text": "\"You&#39;d never know.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 377484.0,
      "end_time": 380954.0,
      "text": "They loved to pat themselves on the back when they could say about a kid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 380978.0,
      "end_time": 385580.0,
      "text": "\"You&#39;d never know he was &#39;delayed&#39; or &#39;autistic&#39; or &#39;different.&#39;\""
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 385604.0,
      "end_time": 389435.0,
      "text": "I could believe that the good path was the path that erased"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 389459.0,
      "end_time": 391648.0,
      "text": "as many differences as possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 392610.0,
      "end_time": 395418.0,
      "text": "Of course, this would have been a disastrous pursuit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 395442.0,
      "end_time": 399669.0,
      "text": "because at the cellular level, my daughter had rare blueprints."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 399693.0,
      "end_time": 402228.0,
      "text": "She wasn&#39;t designed to be like other people."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 402252.0,
      "end_time": 403968.0,
      "text": "She would lead a rare life."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 404465.0,
      "end_time": 408352.0,
      "text": "So, I had another choice: I could drop my story"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 408376.0,
      "end_time": 413657.0,
      "text": "that neurological differences and developmental delays and disabilities"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 413682.0,
      "end_time": 414841.0,
      "text": "were bad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 414865.0,
      "end_time": 420761.0,
      "text": "which means I could also drop my story that a more able-bodied life was better."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 420785.0,
      "end_time": 425688.0,
      "text": "I could release my cultural biases about what made a life good or bad"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 425712.0,
      "end_time": 429296.0,
      "text": "and simply watch my daughter&#39;s life as it unfolded"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 429320.0,
      "end_time": 431832.0,
      "text": "with openness and curiosity."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 432593.0,
      "end_time": 434648.0,
      "text": "One afternoon she was lying on her back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 434672.0,
      "end_time": 437812.0,
      "text": "and she arched her back on the carpet"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 437836.0,
      "end_time": 440788.0,
      "text": "stuck her tongue out of the side of her mouth"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 440812.0,
      "end_time": 444329.0,
      "text": "and managed to torque her body onto her belly."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 444866.0,
      "end_time": 447553.0,
      "text": "Then she tipped over and rolled back onto her back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 447577.0,
      "end_time": 450702.0,
      "text": "and once there, she managed to do it all over again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 450726.0,
      "end_time": 454590.0,
      "text": "rolling and wiggling her 12-pound self under a coffee table."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 454614.0,
      "end_time": 457361.0,
      "text": "At first, I thought she&#39;d gotten stuck there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 457386.0,
      "end_time": 462499.0,
      "text": "but then I saw her reaching for something that her eye had been on all along:"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 462523.0,
      "end_time": 464169.0,
      "text": "a black electric cord."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 464626.0,
      "end_time": 466573.0,
      "text": "She was a year old."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 466598.0,
      "end_time": 471731.0,
      "text": "Other babies her age were for sure pulling up to stand and toddling around,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 471755.0,
      "end_time": 473550.0,
      "text": "some of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 473897.0,
      "end_time": 477408.0,
      "text": "To some, my kid&#39;s situation looked bad:"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 477432.0,
      "end_time": 479329.0,
      "text": "a one-year-old who could only roll."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 479353.0,
      "end_time": 480523.0,
      "text": "But screw that."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 480547.0,
      "end_time": 485247.0,
      "text": "My kid was enjoying the new, limber freedom of mobility."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 485271.0,
      "end_time": 486421.0,
      "text": "I rejoiced."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 487326.0,
      "end_time": 491901.0,
      "text": "Then again, what I watched that afternoon was a baby yanking on an electric cord,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 491925.0,
      "end_time": 493115.0,
      "text": "so you know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 493139.0,
      "end_time": 494705.0,
      "text": "good or bad, hard to say."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 494729.0,
      "end_time": 495878.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 496967.0,
      "end_time": 500770.0,
      "text": "I started seeing that when I released my grip"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 500101.0,
      "end_time": 502444.0,
      "text": "about what made a life good or bad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 502468.0,
      "end_time": 506373.0,
      "text": "I could watch my daughter&#39;s life unfold and see what it was."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 507151.0,
      "end_time": 508555.0,
      "text": "It was beautiful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 508579.0,
      "end_time": 510115.0,
      "text": "it was complicated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 511176.0,
      "end_time": 513275.0,
      "text": "joyful, hard --"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 513299.0,
      "end_time": 519280.0,
      "text": "in other words: just another expression of the human experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 520490.0,
      "end_time": 523687.0,
      "text": "Eventually, my family and I moved to a new state in America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 523711.0,
      "end_time": 527604.0,
      "text": "and we got lucky with a brand-new batch of therapists."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 527628.0,
      "end_time": 531660.0,
      "text": "They didn&#39;t focus on all that was wrong with my kid."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 531900.0,
      "end_time": 534115.0,
      "text": "They didn&#39;t see her differences as problems to fix."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 534139.0,
      "end_time": 536638.0,
      "text": "They acknowledged her limitations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 536662.0,
      "end_time": 539321.0,
      "text": "but they also saw her strengths,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 539345.0,
      "end_time": 542176.0,
      "text": "and they celebrated her for who she was."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 542931.0,
      "end_time": 546439.0,
      "text": "Their goal wasn&#39;t to make Fiona as normal as possible;"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 546463.0,
      "end_time": 550170.0,
      "text": "their goal was simply to help her be as independent as possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 550420.0,
      "end_time": 554355.0,
      "text": "so that she could fulfill her potential, however that looked for her."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 554883.0,
      "end_time": 560511.0,
      "text": "But the culture at large does not take this open attitude about disabilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 560535.0,
      "end_time": 564200.0,
      "text": "We call congenital differences \"birth defects,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 564270.0,
      "end_time": 567505.0,
      "text": "as though human beings were objects on a factory line."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 567878.0,
      "end_time": 570181.0,
      "text": "We might offer pitying expressions"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 570205.0,
      "end_time": 573503.0,
      "text": "when we learn that a colleague had a baby with Down syndrome."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 573527.0,
      "end_time": 577535.0,
      "text": "We hail a blockbuster film about a suicidal wheelchair user,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 577559.0,
      "end_time": 580954.0,
      "text": "despite the fact that actual wheelchair users tell us"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 580978.0,
      "end_time": 584223.0,
      "text": "that stereotype is unfair and damaging."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 584247.0,
      "end_time": 589362.0,
      "text": "And sometimes our medical institutions decide what lives are not worth living."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 589386.0,
      "end_time": 591819.0,
      "text": "Such is the case with Amelia Rivera,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 591843.0,
      "end_time": 594510.0,
      "text": "a girl with my daughter&#39;s same syndrome."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 594760.0,
      "end_time": 597998.0,
      "text": "In 2012, a famous American children&#39;s hospital"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 598220.0,
      "end_time": 602622.0,
      "text": "initially denied Amelia the right to a lifesaving kidney transplant"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 602646.0,
      "end_time": 604610.0,
      "text": "because, according to their form,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 604634.0,
      "end_time": 607503.0,
      "text": "as it said, she was \"mentally retarded.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 607527.0,
      "end_time": 611369.0,
      "text": "This is the way that the story of disabilities as bad manifests"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 611393.0,
      "end_time": 612819.0,
      "text": "in a culture."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 612843.0,
      "end_time": 616659.0,
      "text": "But there&#39;s a surprisingly insidious counterstory --"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 616683.0,
      "end_time": 621330.0,
      "text": "the story, especially, that people with intellectual disabilities are good"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 621354.0,
      "end_time": 624621.0,
      "text": "because they are here to teach us something magical,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 624645.0,
      "end_time": 628953.0,
      "text": "or they are inherently angelic and always sweet."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 628977.0,
      "end_time": 632352.0,
      "text": "You have heard this ableist trope before:"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 632376.0,
      "end_time": 636252.0,
      "text": "the boy with Down syndrome who&#39;s one of God&#39;s special children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 636276.0,
      "end_time": 640104.0,
      "text": "or the girl with the walker and the communication device"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 640129.0,
      "end_time": 641869.0,
      "text": "who is a precious little angel."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 642422.0,
      "end_time": 644729.0,
      "text": "This story rears its head in my daughter&#39;s life"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 644753.0,
      "end_time": 645998.0,
      "text": "around Christmastime,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 646220.0,
      "end_time": 648406.0,
      "text": "when certain people get positively giddy"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 648430.0,
      "end_time": 651636.0,
      "text": "at the thought of seeing her in angel&#39;s wings and a halo"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 651660.0,
      "end_time": 653880.0,
      "text": "at the pageant."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 653112.0,
      "end_time": 658568.0,
      "text": "The insinuation is that these people don&#39;t experience the sticky complexities"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 658592.0,
      "end_time": 660520.0,
      "text": "of being human."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 660457.0,
      "end_time": 662934.0,
      "text": "And although at times, especially as a baby,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 662958.0,
      "end_time": 666146.0,
      "text": "my daughter has, in fact, looked angelic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 666171.0,
      "end_time": 668505.0,
      "text": "she has grown into the type of kid"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 668529.0,
      "end_time": 671814.0,
      "text": "who does the rascally things that any other kid does,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 671838.0,
      "end_time": 676819.0,
      "text": "such as when she, at age four, shoved her two-year-old sister."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 677643.0,
      "end_time": 680894.0,
      "text": "My girl deserves the right to annoy the hell out of you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 680918.0,
      "end_time": 682277.0,
      "text": "like any other kid."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 683532.0,
      "end_time": 687650.0,
      "text": "When we label a person tragic or angelic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 687890.0,
      "end_time": 689179.0,
      "text": "bad or good,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 689203.0,
      "end_time": 691132.0,
      "text": "we rob them of their humanity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 691750.0,
      "end_time": 696210.0,
      "text": "along with not only the messiness and complexity that that title brings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 696450.0,
      "end_time": 698623.0,
      "text": "but the rights and dignities as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 700228.0,
      "end_time": 702790.0,
      "text": "My girl does not exist to teach me things"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 702814.0,
      "end_time": 704231.0,
      "text": "or any of us things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 704255.0,
      "end_time": 706417.0,
      "text": "but she has indeed taught me:"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 706441.0,
      "end_time": 709423.0,
      "text": "number one, how many mozzarella cheese sticks"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 709447.0,
      "end_time": 712915.0,
      "text": "a 22-pound human being can consume in one day --"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 712939.0,
      "end_time": 715488.0,
      "text": "which is five, for the record;"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 715512.0,
      "end_time": 720703.0,
      "text": "and two, the gift of questioning my culture&#39;s beliefs"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 720727.0,
      "end_time": 722946.0,
      "text": "about what makes a life good"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 722970.0,
      "end_time": 724587.0,
      "text": "and what makes life bad."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 724990.0,
      "end_time": 727966.0,
      "text": "If you had told me six years ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 727990.0,
      "end_time": 731615.0,
      "text": "that my daughter would sometimes use and iPad app to communicate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 731639.0,
      "end_time": 733909.0,
      "text": "I might have thought that was sad."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 734644.0,
      "end_time": 738240.0,
      "text": "But now I recall the first day I handed Fiona her iPad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 738264.0,
      "end_time": 740981.0,
      "text": "loaded with a thousand words,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 741500.0,
      "end_time": 746143.0,
      "text": "each represented by a tiny little icon or little square on her iPad app."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 746167.0,
      "end_time": 749305.0,
      "text": "And I recall how bold and hopeful it felt,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 749329.0,
      "end_time": 754463.0,
      "text": "even as some of her therapists said that my expectations were way too high,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 754487.0,
      "end_time": 757823.0,
      "text": "that she would never be able to hit those tiny targets."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 758276.0,
      "end_time": 762468.0,
      "text": "And I recall watching in awe as she gradually learned"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 762493.0,
      "end_time": 764662.0,
      "text": "to flex her little thumb"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 764686.0,
      "end_time": 767738.0,
      "text": "and hit the buttons to say words she loved,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 767762.0,
      "end_time": 770761.0,
      "text": "like \"reggae\" and \"cheese\""
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 770785.0,
      "end_time": 774300.0,
      "text": "and a hundred other words she loved that her mouth couldn&#39;t yet say."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 775216.0,
      "end_time": 778113.0,
      "text": "And then we had to teach her less-fun words, prepositions --"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 778137.0,
      "end_time": 781210.0,
      "text": "words like \"of\" and \"on\" and \"in.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 781460.0,
      "end_time": 783316.0,
      "text": "And we worked on this for a few weeks."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 783340.0,
      "end_time": 786740.0,
      "text": "And then I recall sitting at a dining room table"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 786764.0,
      "end_time": 788745.0,
      "text": "with many relatives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 788769.0,
      "end_time": 791879.0,
      "text": "and, apropos of absolutely nothing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 791903.0,
      "end_time": 795328.0,
      "text": "Fiona used her iPad app to say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 795352.0,
      "end_time": 798170.0,
      "text": "\"poop in toilet.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 798194.0,
      "end_time": 799428.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 800168.0,
      "end_time": 802240.0,
      "text": "Good or bad, hard to say."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 802480.0,
      "end_time": 803198.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 803584.0,
      "end_time": 805960.0,
      "text": "My kid is human, that&#39;s all."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 805985.0,
      "end_time": 807559.0,
      "text": "And that is a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 808268.0,
      "end_time": 809545.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 809569.0,
      "end_time": 813401.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}